{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> &quot;The Mist&quot; is a text association decryption game. The game has 8 chapters, 40+ puzzles, which can be decrypted by associating with the text prompts of each level and combining with the current scene.<br></li><li> The game tells the story of my last year, but I won't tell you details.<br>It was not easy.<br></li><li> Go ahead and experience it yourself.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Instruction</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The game has 8 chapters: Outset, Frustration, Confusion, Go Astray, Failure, Pressure, Desperation, Hope.<br></li><li> Each chapter has 5-6 levels.<br></li><li> A sentence will appear at each level. Players need to find the right way to pass the level through association, reasoning and judgment.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tips</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make sure to turn on the volume.<br></li><li> Be patient.<br></li><li> Challenge yourself.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048470/extras/StatisticsUpdateText_EN.jpg?t=1554012116\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048470/extras/Statistics_EN_600w.jpg?t=1554012116\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048470/extras/Warning_EN.jpg?t=1554012116\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Other languages</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> For other languages, you can translate by yourself.<br></li><li> Add new language file to TheMist/TheMist_Data/StreamingAssets/Data/Languages<br></li><li> Don't forget to add new textures at TheMist/TheMist_Data/StreamingAssets/Data/Textures</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Non-repetitive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1048470/443f9c4668de84fd7464c166e02d5df09ab114f1.jpg"},{"name":"Look for","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstat